SQL_STMT_U.val: SELECT g.Ebene1, g.Ebene2, g.Ebene3, g.Ebene4, g.BETREIBER, (CASE WHEN isnull(m.ModellBezeichnungExtern, '') = '' THEN ISNULL(g.ModellBezeichnung, '') ELSE isnull(m.ModellbezeichnungExtern, '') END) AS modell, g.IDNR, ISNULL(iz.Hostname, '') AS Hostname, ISNULL(iz.IPAdresse, '') AS IPAdresse, ISNULL(g.Serien_Nr, '') AS Seriennummer, ISNULL(h.Bezeichnung, 'ohne') AS Hersteller, ISNULL(k.Name_I, '') AS Name1, ISNULL(k.Name_II, '') AS Name2, ISNULL(k.Name_III, '') AS Name3, ISNULL(k.Strasse, '') AS Strasse, ISNULL(k.Ort, '') AS Ort, ISNULL(k.Matchcode, '') AS Matchcode, ISNULL(g.Standort, '') AS Standort, idz.RO_Kostenstelle AS Kostenstelle, null AS LetzterTonerLevelDatum, g.ModellBezeichnung, iz.MACAdresse, idz.Gebaeude, idz.Stockwerk, idz.Raum, ISNULL(idz.TELEFONNUMMER, '') AS Telefonnr, ISNULL(idz.EMail, '') AS EMail, g.InstallDatum, ISNULL(g.Ansprechpartner, '') AS Partner, ISNULL(k.Plz, 0) AS Plz, g.ModellNummer, g.Fachhndler_Nr, g.ReferenzNr1, g.ReferenzNr2, g.ReferenzNr3, iz.Bemerkung, g.Kunden_Referenznummer, scf.lastDeviceStatusUpdate, dev.letztesUpdate, idz.KontaktpersonGeraet, idz.KontaktpersonVBM FROM dbo.GERAETE AS g WITH(NOLOCK) INNER JOIN dbo.SM_KONTAKT_KUNDE smk WITH(NOLOCK) on smk.Ebene1=g.Ebene1 and smk.Ebene2=g.Ebene2 and smk.Ebene3=g.Ebene3 and smk.Ebene4=g.Ebene4 and smk.KDNR=g.Betreiber and smk.Projekt=:5 and smk.EmailAdresse=':6' and smk.Aktiv=1 INNER JOIN dbo.EBENE4 AS e WITH(NOLOCK) ON g.Ebene1 = e.Ebene1 AND g.Ebene2 = e.Ebene2 AND g.Ebene3 = e.Ebene3 AND g.Ebene4 = e.Ebene4 INNER JOIN dbo.GERAETE_ZUSATZ AS iz WITH(NOLOCK) ON g.Ebene1 = iz.Ebene1 AND g.Ebene2 = iz.Ebene2 AND g.Ebene3 = iz.Ebene3 AND g.Ebene4 = iz.Ebene4 AND g.IDNR = iz.IDNR LEFT OUTER JOIN dbo.IDNR_ZUSATZ AS idz WITH(NOLOCK) ON g.Ebene1 = idz.Ebene1 AND g.Ebene2 = idz.Ebene2 AND g.Ebene3 = idz.Ebene3 AND g.Ebene4 = idz.Ebene4 AND g.IDNR = idz.IDNR LEFT OUTER JOIN dbo.MODELL AS m WITH(NOLOCK) ON m.Ebene1 = e.ZentralEbene1 AND m.Ebene2 = e.ZentralEbene2 AND m.Ebene3 = e.ZentralEbene3 AND m.Ebene4 = e.ZentralEbene4 AND g.ModellNummer = m.ModellNr LEFT OUTER JOIN dbo.HERSTELLER AS h WITH(NOLOCK) ON g.Ebene1 = h.Ebene1 AND g.Ebene2 = h.Ebene2 AND g.Ebene3 = h.Ebene3 AND g.Ebene4 = h.Ebene4 AND m.hersteller = h.Hersteller left outer join dbo.SCFleet_device scf WITH(NOLOCK) on g.Ebene1 =scf.Ebene1 and g.Ebene2 =scf.Ebene2 and g.Ebene3 =scf.Ebene3 and g.Ebene4 =scf.Ebene4 and g.SC_DeviceID=scf.deviceid left outer join dbo.Device_WS_SQL dev WITH(NOLOCK) on g.Ebene1= dev.Ebene1 and g.Ebene2= dev.Ebene2 and g.Ebene3= dev.Ebene3 and g.Ebene4= dev.Ebene4 and g.Berechnungsinterva=dev.deviceid LEFT OUTER JOIN dbo.KUNDEN AS k WITH(NOLOCK) ON k.Ebene1 = CASE WHEN g.ZentralerBetreiber = 1 THEN e.ZentralEbene1 ELSE g.Ebene1 END AND k.Ebene2 = CASE WHEN g.ZentralerBetreiber = 1 THEN e.ZentralEbene2 ELSE g.Ebene2 END AND k.Ebene3 = CASE WHEN g.ZentralerBetreiber = 1 THEN e.ZentralEbene3 ELSE g.Ebene3 END AND k.Ebene4 = CASE WHEN g.ZentralerBetreiber = 1 THEN e.ZentralEbene4 ELSE g.Ebene4 END AND k.KDNR= g.BETREIBER WHERE g.Ebene1=:1 and g.Ebene2=:2 and g.Ebene3=:3 and g.Ebene4=:4 :7
